  "corporate_actions_text": "Equity History\nPrefs\nDividend\nSplit\nMerger\nRight\nDate\tDetails\n\n2024\nMay 15\n\t\nSub Division of the Face Value\nStock split from Rs.10 to Rs.2 per share with effect from may 15, 2024.\n\n\n2021\nAug 24\n\t\nQualified Institutional Placement\n167392032 shares have been allotted at a premium of Rs.139.35 per share to QIBs pursuan to Qualified Insttutional Placement.\n\n\n2020\nDec 11\n\t\nQualified Institutional Placement\n193236714 shares have been allotted at a premium of Rs.93.50 per share to Eligible Qualified Institutional Buyers.\n\n\n2020\nApr 01\n\t\nScheme of Amalgamation\n423268155 shares have been allotted pursuant to the Scheme of Amalgmation of Syndicate Bank into Canara Bank.\n\n\n2019\nDec 04\n\t\nIssued to Government of India\n276988576 shares have been allotted at a premium of Rs.227.23 per share to Government of India on preferential basis.\n\n\n2019\nFeb 06\n\t\nIssued under ESPS\n20000000 shares have been allotted at a premium of Rs.176 per share under ESPS.\n\n\n2018\nMar 27\n\t\nIssued to Government of India\n135954616 shares have been allotted at a premium of Rs.347.84 per share to Government of India on Prferential basis.\n\n\n2017\nFeb 17\n\t\nRights Issue\n\n\n2015\nSep 30\n\t\nIssued to GOI\n27794083 shares have been allotted to the President of India (GOI) on Preferential basis.\n\n\n2015\nMay 12\n\t\nPreferential Issue Of Shares\n40000000 shares have been allotted at a premium of Rs.370.08 per share.\n\n\n2015\nMar 31\n\t\nIssued to GOI\n13938134 shares have been allotted at a premium of RS.398.95 per share to Government of India on preferential basis.\n\n\n2013\nDec 31\n\t\nPreferential Issue Of Shares\n18258837 shares have been allotted on preferential basis to President of India.\n\n\n2011\nMar 15\n\t\nIssued to QIBs\n33000000 shares have been allotted at a premium of Rs.594 per share to QIBs.\n\n\n2002\nDec 20\n\t\nPublic Issue"
